videos.headline: Evans knocks down the smooth jumper
videos.description: Louisville jumps out early with Dana Evans sinking the jump shot.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Evans knocks down the smooth jumper) 2021/03/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Balogun, Evans connect on buzzer-beater
videos.description: Dana Evans skillfully dishes the pass to Elizabeth Balogun for the layup just as the end of the halftime buzzer.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Balogun, Evans connect on buzzer-beater) 2021/03/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Prince blocks Dixon at the rim
videos.description: Oregon's Sedona Prince denies Elizabeth Dixon's attempt to drive in for a layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Prince blocks Dixon at the rim) 2021/03/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Evans drains an NBA-range 3
videos.description: Louisville's Dana Evans can score from distance as she blazes the net with a 3-pointer from distance.

videos.headline: Robinson sends behind-the-back pass to Evans for the bucket
videos.description: Louisville seals the win with the fast-break connection from Mykasa Robinson to Dana Evans.
